room_title: Escape room "Medieval Marauders" by Race City Escapes in Mooresville
room_description: The king has died. He cared deeply for his cherished kingdom. He chose a leader from each of the four neighboring factions. Knowing that the lust for power would be a factor he hid the identity of his chosen benefactor inside the room.  It is your job to find out who it is, eliminate the other factions to be able to claim the throne, and stop the Crusaders from taking control.
